<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="author" content="">
    <link rel="icon" href="/static/favicon.ico">

    <title>PriceYakalytics</title>

    <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.12.4/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.js"></script>
    <style>
      body {
        padding-top: 30px;
      }
      .logo{
        height: 60px;
      }
      .login-logo{
          height:45px;
      }
      .login-text{
          font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
          margin-left: 5px;
          font-size: 1.3em;
          display: inline-block;
          vertical-align: middle;
      }
      .container{
          border-color: rgba(0, 132, 255, 1);
          border-width: 2px;
          border-radius: 15px;
          background-color: rgba(0, 132, 255, 0.1);
          height: 350px;
      }
      .content{
          margin-top: 50px;
          margin-bottom: 50px;
      }
      p{
        font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      .row{
          margin-top: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-4 col-md-6 col-md-offset-4">
            <img class="logo" src="PriceYakalytics.png">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-4 col-md-6 col-md-offset-4 explain">
                <p>Easily add a Google Analytics tracking pixel to your PriceYak Listings!
                <p>To get started, log in below. <a href="https://community.ebay.com/t5/Tools-Apps/How-to-Track-eBay-Listing-with-Google-Analytics-Beginers-Guide/td-p/27194223" target="_blank">Inspired by this eBay blog post.</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-4 col-md-6 col-md-offset-4">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" type="button" class="btn btn-default">
                    <img class="login-logo" src="logo_small.png">
                    <span class="login-text">Login with Priceyak</span>
                </a>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>
